    {
      "id": "interaction-policy-note-ownership",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Ownership Model",
      "position": {
        "x": 2147.333333333333,
        "y": -399
      },
      "width": 420,
      "height": 220,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Hover Ownership Model\n\n- **Browser owns mechanics**: native text, links, buttons, inputs, and CSS hover behavior.\n- **Graph owns geometry**: which node, handle, edge, or background zone is spatially under the pointer.\n- **Editor owns meaning**: what hover reveals, which affordances are active, and how interaction mode changes behavior.\n\nNode components may declare zones, but they should not independently own global hover truth.",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
        "html": "",
        "svg": "",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
