    {
      "id": "interaction-policy-note-zones",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Zone Model",
      "position": {
        "x": 1397,
        "y": -415
      },
      "width": 360,
      "height": 240,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Zone Model\n\nEvery node should declare a small shared set of zones:\n\n- shell\n- content\n- controls\n- drag affordance\n- resize handles\n- ports\n\nZones are allowed to differ in cursor and pointer-event behavior. They are not allowed to overlap in a way that gives the same pixel multiple primary roles.",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
        "html": "",
        "svg": "",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "identity": {
