    {
      "id": "interaction-policy-note-invariants",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Invariants",
      "position": {
        "x": 3091,
        "y": 1115
      },
      "width": 360,
      "height": 260,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Invariants\n\n- One interaction role per pixel.\n- Hidden elements do not receive pointer events.\n- Hover does not create a new owner under a stationary cursor.\n- Parent shells yield to child interactive content.\n- Production and dev should obey the same interaction law.",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
        "html": "",
        "svg": "",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
