    {
      "id": "interaction-policy-note-precedence",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Hover Precedence",
      "position": {
        "x": 1660.333333333333,
        "y": 645
      },
      "width": 380,
      "height": 300,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Hover Precedence\n\nWhen multiple zones could plausibly own the same pixel, resolve them in this order:\n\n1. active drag / resize / rotate interaction\n2. visible interactive controls\n3. text/content regions\n4. visible ports / handles when available\n5. explicit drag affordances\n6. neutral node shell\n7. graph background\n\nHover decoration may appear from ownership, but it must not change ownership under a stationary cursor.",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
        "html": "",
        "svg": "",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "identity": {
            "graphId": "markdown_class",
            "name": "markdown Node Class",
            "version": "0.1.0",
            "description": "Canonical markdown content node.",
            "createdAt": "2026-02-24T20:05:15Z",
            "updatedAt": "2026-03-24T01:20:00.000Z"
          },
          "intent": "graph",
          "meaning": "Canonical markdown content node.",
          "description": "Canonical markdown content node.",
          "defaults": {},
          "nodeDef": {
            "key": "markdown",
            "ref": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
            "source": "local",
            "version": ">=0.1.0"
          },
          "views": [
            {
              "key": "markdown",
              "intent": "editor",
              "payload": "editor.web",
              "ref": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
